  background: {fileID: 0}
  lines:
  - speakerName: Xuan
    englishSpeakerName: Xuan
    text: Day la dialogue test trong scene UI. Nhan E de sang cau tiep theo.
    englishText: This is a dialogue test in the scene UI. Press E to move to the
      next line.
    portrait: {fileID: -4254258901546231152, guid: c5d997eca51e38d418373f1e8fdc90ce, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Meo
    englishSpeakerName: Cat
    text: Panel nay co nen rieng, o chan dung, ten nhan vat va vung text duoc can
      san.
    englishText: This panel has its own background, portrait slot, speaker name,
      and aligned text area.
    portrait: {fileID: -4254258901546231152, guid: c5d997eca51e38d418373f1e8fdc90ce, type: 3}
  - speakerName: Xuan
    englishSpeakerName: Xuan
    text: Het doan test thi dialogue se an. Sau nay minh chi can thay du lieu that
      vao DialogueSO.
    englishText: After the test sequence ends, the dialogue hides. Later we only
      need to swap real data into the DialogueSO.
    portrait: {fileID: -4254258901546231152, guid: c5d997eca51e38d418373f1e8fdc90ce, type: 3}
